Class OhapServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.henrikhedberg.ohap.OhapServer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HbdpOhapServer, TcpOhapServer

    public abstract class OhapServer
extends java.lang.Object
    Open Home Automation Protocol (OHAP) server. A subclass must implement a method to accept connections and instantiate OhapSessions.

    1.2 (20160312)
